                                         'default.\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         'Use only when:\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         '- Codex is the current owner\n'
                                         '- Review has passed\n'
                                         '- No Required Fixes remain\n'
                                         '- User has approved finalization or One-Shot '
                                         'Review-Finalize-Next requires a local checkpoint\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         'Required checks:\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         '```bash\n'
                                         'git status\n'
                                         'git diff --name-only HEAD\n'
                                         'python scripts/check_progress_docs.py\n'
                                         'python scripts/git_finalize_check.py\n'
                                         '```\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         'Then:\n'
                                         '\n'
                                         '1. Confirm no secrets are included.\n'
                                         '2. Commit locally:\n'
                                         '   ```bash\n'
                                         '   git add -A\n'
                                         '   git commit -m "..."\n'
                                         '   ```\n'
                                         '3. Do not push unless the user explicitly approves or '
                                         'standing approval exists.\n'
                                         '4. If push is approved:\n'
                                         '   ```bash\n'
                                         '   git push\n'
                                         '   ```\n'
