                                    '## Dual-Agent Development Philosophy\n'
                                    '\n'
                                    'This project uses Codex and Claude Code together:\n'
                                    '\n'
                                    '- Codex brainstorms with the user and converts ideas into '
                                    'structured change requests or implementation briefs.\n'
                                    '- Claude Code implements the approved brief.\n'
                                    '- Codex reviews the implementation and performs local git '
                                    'checkpoints after review passes.\n'
                                    '- User remains the final product owner and acceptance '
                                    'authority.\n',
